title: Xshapes

creator: xshapes app
descriptionHtml: XSHAPES APP is your best friend for achieving a healthy lifestyle. Regardless of your goals or circumstances, we help you reach them in a simple and fun way. Our community offers over 50 workout guides and hundreds of customizable workouts, as well as a recipe bank with over 500 family-friendly and balanced options (standard, vegan, and vegetarian). You also get access to a wealth of educational material and the ability to track your progress. With our workout plans and exercise library, you can tailor your training to your needs and preferences. No matter who you are, what your goals are, or where you train, there is a plan for you!
descriptionShort: Your pocket sized personal trainer, no matter what your goals are!

title: Xshapes

creator: Gym & Fitness Sverige AB
descriptionHtml:
Join Livity and gain access to a training experience that brings you closer to your goals in a sustainable and healthy way.

TRAINING PROGRAMS FOR ALL GOALS: Regardless of your goals or preferred form of exercise, Livity has a training program that suits you. Our customizable training programs are designed to fit all goals and levels, whether you're working out at home or at the gym.

FOLLOW ALONG CLASSES & HUNDREDS OF INDIVIDUAL SESSIONS: As a user, you get full access to hundreds of individual workout sessions. Perfect for those who enjoy variety in their training or want to combine their training program with follow-along sessions.

TRACK YOUR PROGRESS: Plan your workouts on the calendar and track your progress over time. We believe in creating long-term habits that last a lifetime. In the app, you also have the option to record your measurements and physical development over time.

RECIPES FOR THE WHOLE FAMILY: Explore our extensive recipe bank with delicious and healthy meals, perfect for the whole family. Fuel your body with nutritious food that supports your fitness journey.

INSTRUCTIONAL VIDEOS & EXERCISE DESCRIPTIONS: Get detailed exercise descriptions and instructional videos to ensure correct technique and maximum effectiveness for each workout.

FEEL SECURE WITH LIVITY: We believe in nutrition and exercise for life. We believe in sustainable and healthy results. In the app, you get full access to plenty of nutrition and training advice, as well as access to the app's Q/A function and chat, where you have direct contact with the team.

Download Livity today and embark on your journey toward a stronger, healthier version of yourself. Regardless of where you are in your fitness journey, we have the tools to help you reach your goals!
descriptionShort: Nutrition & workouts for life - Reach a healthy and sustainable lifestyle!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Hi! We're excited to let you know about our latest update. This update includes bug fixes and performance improvements to make your experience better.

title:
Livity
4.0.6

creator: Gym & Fitness Sverige AB
descriptionHtml:
Join Livity and gain access to a nutrition and fitness experience that brings you closer to your goals in a sustainable and healthy way.

We believe in a healthy lifestyle that allows you to enjoy life while working out, feeling great, and achieving your goals – no matter what they are or what your daily routine looks like. Exercising should be fun, and you should be able to eat a lot of delicious food while having a plan. Whether you want to lose weight, build muscle, or simply feel good.

In the app, you will have full access to:

HUNDREDS OF DELICIOUS RECIPES: Discover our extensive recipe library with tasty and healthy meals, perfect for the whole family. You’ll find everything from delicious desserts to your favorite pizza and classic dishes to simple meals for your lunchboxes.

TRACK YOUR DIET: With the app's built-in scanner, you can easily log your food intake and ensure you’re eating in line with your goals. You can choose to log individual foods directly or one of our recipes, giving you full control over your daily intake.

WORKOUT PROGRAMS FOR ALL GOALS: Whether you want to get stronger, start running, work out at home, strengthen your body during pregnancy, try Pilates, or shape your body, there’s a workout program for you. You'll have full access to over 100 workout programs designed for all levels and can be done both at home and in the gym.

FOLLOW ALONG CLASSES & HUNDREDS OF INDIVIDUAL WORKOUTS: Perfect for those who want variety in their training or complement their workout schedule with engaging follow-along sessions. You can also create your own workouts directly in the app!

TRACK YOUR PROGRESS: Plan your workouts in the calendar and monitor your results over time. Log your body measurements and physical development to see your progress and stay motivated. We help you create sustainable workout habits for life.

INSTRUCTIONAL VIDEOS & EXERCISE DESCRIPTIONS: Learn correct techniques with our detailed instructional videos and exercise descriptions. Maximize the effectiveness of each workout and minimize the risk of injury by performing the exercises correctly.

FEEL SECURE WITH LIVITY: We believe in a holistic approach to health that combines nutrition and exercise for sustainable results. In the app, you’ll have access to a wealth of nutrition and workout advice, and you can easily contact our team through the Q/A function and chat for personal support.

Download Livity today and start your journey towards a stronger, healthier version of yourself. No matter where you are in your fitness journey, we have the tools to help you achieve your goals!
descriptionShort: Nutrition & workouts for life - Reach a healthy and sustainable lifestyle!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Better diet registrations, user experience optimization and bug fixes.
